  "message": "Replace tests that don't reproduce assertion failure\n\n- Remove replace-sliced-array, replace-numeric-with-null, and\n  replace-with-null-preserves-existing tests (these don't actually\n  trigger the assertion failure on main)\n- Add replace-with-null-ocsf test that reproduces the original bug\n  using ocsf::cast with existing null values in input\n- Format test files for readability\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
